SIMPLE: stinging
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stinging
<hw>Sting"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Piercing, or capable
of piercing, with a sting; inflicting acute pain as if with a sting,
goad, or pointed weapon; pungent; biting; <as>as, <ex>stinging</ex>
cold; a <ex>stinging</ex> rebuke.</as></def> --
<wordforms><wf>Sting"ing*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Stinging cell</b></col>. <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <cd>Same as
<cref>Lasso cell</cref>, under <er>Lasso</er>.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stingless</ent>⟦br⟧
